Current planned changes to improve safety are a result of the latest 7/10/2018 Process Hazard Analysis (PHA).  A summary is provided below; a detailed schedule is kept on-site.  The improvements were expected to be completed by 1/11/2019:



-    Administrative and documentation improvements;

-    Re-check and re-secure water supply points;

-    Minor mechanical improvements and off-season maintenance considerations;

-    Continued management awareness regarding Human Error potentials;

-    Continued portable equipment placement awareness including barrier placement for equipment and piping protection.





